content.rendered:
Directed by Shahad Nilambur

Written by Dhyan Sreenivasan

Star Dileesh Pothan (Prakashan). Mathew Thomas (Das Prakashan). Dhyan Sreenivasan (Suni). Aju Varghese (Musthafa). Saiju Kurup (Kuttan). Ritunjay Sreejith (Akhil Prakash). Sreejith Ravi (Raghavan). Nisha Sarangh (Latha). Sminu Sijo (Lalitha). Govind V. Pai (Anwar). Ganga G. Nair (Anwar’s Mother). Malavika Manoj (Neethu). Azmiya (Sruthy (as Azmiya Aslam)). Ashwin Jose (Shoaib). Unni Raja (Salam). Tinu Thomas (Hospital PRO). Pranav Yesudas (Dileepan (as Pranav)). Shabin T.V. (Physical Trainer). Kookal Raghavan (School Principal). Mahima Radhakrishnan (Minu). Nithin Sabu (Manu). Vijayakrishnan A.B. (Shibu Kuttan (as Vijayakrishnan))

Language Malayalam

Producers Visakh Subramaniam. Tinu Thomas. Aju Varghese

Production Funtastic Films .Hit Makers Entertainments
